    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">Refinement of :OTF -- just bank (with no keyword) will clear the specified group.<br>Improvement: ':[#]OTFG[!] &lt;register&gt;' which will copy contents of specifed group to specified register.This means that you can &quot;:2OTFG y&quot; to copy the search pattern used by highlight group 2 into register y.</td>
</tr>
